    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 engine. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to reach a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity, complemented by a functional Electronic Damping Control (EDC) system and an M Variable Differential Lock that provides superb lateral traction during high-G cornering. Maintenance is current, including the critical rod bearing and throttle actuator services. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain remains robust and the carbon fiber roof integrity is perfect. A precision-engineered machine optimized for the purist.",
