    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-performing driver. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a deep gloss, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014standard signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one, and the interior retains a fresh, neutral scent. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a complete folder of records included. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, new filters, and a cooling system flush. The tires offer plenty of grip for several seasons to come, and the transmission shifts with crisp, factory-spec precision. This is a well-sorted, honest car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 33800.0,
